longBusinessSummary: GERRY WEBER International AG operates as a fashion and lifestyle company worldwide. It operates through two segments, Wholesale and Retail. The company engages in the design, production, wholesale, and retail of ladies wear. It offers T-shirts, knitwear, blouses, blazers, trousers, dresses, skirts, and jackets/coats; and accessories, such as wallets, bags, and scarves/shawls, as well as shoes. The company provides its products under the GERRY WEBER, TAIFUN, and SAMOON brand families through retail stores and online shops. As of December 31, 2020, it operated 569 retail stores; 241 franchised stores; and 1,754 shop-in-shops. The company was founded in 1973 and is headquartered in Halle, Germany.
